Hello Brandie, I have a great mystery shop open for you this week at Salt Life in Foley, AL. You MAY NOT see this shop on our website, so contact me if you are interested.

You will have an interaction with an employee where you will get help finding something to try on in the dressing room. The purpose of this shop is to evaluate the interaction with the employees and the cleanliness of the store, including the dressing room. You do NOT need to make a purchase, but if you do, you will also evaluate the cashier experience.

This shop pays [financial_data]

Please respond to this email letting me know what date works for sure, or login and request this shop on our website.

Thanks and Take Care ~Amy
